                    "text": "You may choose to settle the case with the complainant. This can be a quicker and simpler way to resolve the dispute. To settle the case, you may approach the complainant directly, or you may sign up for a Lok Adalat/Mediation Session that is overseen by the court. You may find more information about Lok Adalat here <bit.ly.>.",
                    "style": "annexure-text"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "If you choose to settle the case, you may inform the court after joining the case on the Portal.",
                    "style": "annexure-text"
